pry into my privacy

111
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,560
without permission?

112
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:50,399
I've been striving
for your cause wholeheartedly.

113
00:07:50,399 --> 00:07:52,639
I thought you'd at least
be frank with me.

114
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:54,560
