I only feel something tough.

131
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:18,679
Sorry about that.

132
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:21,399
One must always
carry something for self-defense.

133
00:09:23,679 --> 00:09:24,960
Don't mind it.

134
00:09:33,879 --> 00:09:34,840
How about now?

135
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:37,919
